      "name": "spring-rest-send-with-metadata",
      "prompt": "Invoke axon4to5-migrate at $SKILL_DIR with `framework=axoniq configuration=spring mode=single source=$SOURCE`. OrderRestController is a Spring @RestController. It imports AF4 CommandGateway (org.axonframework.commandhandling.gateway.CommandGateway) and returns `commandGateway.send(command, RequestContext.with(userId))` from a `CompletableFuture<Void>` method. Apply the command-gateway recipe: (1) swap the CommandGateway import to AF5 (org.axonframework.messaging.commandhandling.gateway.CommandGateway), (2) append .resultAs(Void.class) to the send call so the return type compiles. Field type, constructor, and method signature stay the same. Copy the Result block to $WORKSPACE/result.md.",
